00:26:38,096 --> 00:26:39,664
Yes, it'd be the best.

553
00:26:39,731 --> 00:26:41,766
This is incredible.

554
00:26:41,833 --> 00:26:43,368
This must be their main dish.

555
00:26:43,435 --> 00:26:45,270
TRIPE GOMTANG

556
00:26:46,037 --> 00:26:49,474
Making tripe gomtang
is a very tricky process.

557
00:26:49,541 --> 00:26:53,612
First, the intestines have to be boiled.

558
00:26:54,212 --> 00:26:58,783
