00:31:46,037 --> 00:31:47,572
So it has a clean flavor.

659
00:31:53,144 --> 00:31:55,647
It's like a pot from the old TV show,
"Today's Dish."

660
00:31:55,713 --> 00:31:56,547
You're right.

