00:31:59,651 --> 00:32:02,854
The traditional dish is dumpling soup.

662
00:32:02,921 --> 00:32:05,356
Jeongol is a dish that
was developed from that.

663
00:32:05,423 --> 00:32:06,925
It has more variety.

664
00:32:06,991 --> 00:32:10,395
