00:49:56,159 --> 00:49:59,629
Kids eat ramyeon with triangle gimbap
at convenience stores.

1005
00:49:59,696 --> 00:50:02,232
And they'll probably want broth
even when they're older.

1006
00:50:02,299 --> 00:50:04,901
This shows that

1007
00:50:04,968 --> 00:50:07,738
all generations love broth.

1008
00:50:07,804 --> 00:50:10,374
There's a saying that Koreans
need rice to carry on with life.

1009
00:50:10,807 --> 00:50:13,477
A thought occurred to me
while we were on this gukbap trip.

1010
00:50:13,543 --> 00:50:16,713
Soup is actually what kept us going.

1011
00:50:17,314 --> 00:50:20,817
Soup is the great force
that makes us eat rice.

1012
00:50:20,884 --> 00:50:23,253
Because we had soup,
we had the strength to carry on.

1013
00:50:24,588 --> 00:50:25,655
Take gukbap as an example.

1014
00:50:25,722 --> 00:50:26,923
It's soup and rice.

1015
00:50:26,990 --> 00:50:29,860
It made me think that

1016
00:50:29,926 --> 00:50:31,561
soup is what empowers us.

